headline: MSCI Launches Global Classification Standards for Private Assets
summary: NEW YORK, October 07, 2025--Private assets are growing rapidly, fueled by institutional allocations and increasing flows from private wealth. Yet the industry remains constrained by a lack of transparency, with no common system to effectively classify exposures, measure performance or communicate strategies.
